{"type":"message","id":"fe261acb","parentId":"2e5d8de0","timestamp":"2026-06-01T00:19:48.300Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_akAX0NLEgqIlBsmjxZKb7559","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# User.md — 用户画像\n\n## 基本信息\n- **称呼:** 宋志红\n- **QQ号:** EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A\n- **bot通道:** bot4\n- **首次对话:** 2026-05-29 16:45\n- **语气偏好:** \n- **技术水平:** \n\n## 兴趣与喜好\n- \n\n## 常用功能\n- \n\n## 对话中提到的关键信息\n- 和汀桑（李汀生）是一家人 \n\n## 对话风格说明\n- \n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780273188299}}
